    <note type="biography">
        <p>French socialist. Founded the <hi rend="italic">Journal du progrès</hi> in 1839. Published his first book, <hi rend="italic">Organisation du travail</hi>, in 1840. Made member of provisional French government in February 1848. Forced into exile, living in London, after the riots in Paris of May 1848. Returned to Paris and re-entered French political life in 1870.</p></note>
